data.title: Heber City Storage
data.meta_description: Heber City Storage offers special pricing on all available self storage units in Heber City. Visit us online and reserve your storage unit!
data.text:
Store with Ease

Heber City Storage is not only the newest facility for self storage in Heber City and all other surrounding areas; we have the Best Customer Service around. If you are looking for clean and quality storage in a variety of different sizes, you have come to the right place. We have storage lockers and storage units ranging from as small as 5x5 to as large as 12x41. We also offer standard drive-up units and dual access units for your convenience.

A Better Value

Saving you time and money is our mission. We offer a selection of property features designed to maximize the efficiency of our facility. Included in that are Climate Controlled Units, State-of-the-Art Storage, Clean & Affordable Storage Units, No Long Term Contract, High Security Cylinder Locks, Roll Up Doors, Dual Access Storage Units. Our lease terms are also flexible, so you know youâre getting the best value.

Convenient Location

Our state-of-the-art storage facility is located right near the intersection of US-40 and US-189, just south of downtown Heber City. We offer extended gate access hours 365 days a year, and our office is open five days a week. Our manager lives on-site and is available after hours by phone for any questions or concerns you may have regarding your storage experience.

RV & Boat Parking

Need extra parking spaces? We have ample indoor insulated parking for trucks, trailers, cars, snowmobiles, RVs or boat parking. Opened in 2010 with new buildings added in 2014, Heber City Storage has everything you need for efficient storage at reasonable prices. Sign up to reserve your storage unit now and receive a free high security lock with your move-in.

Reserve your space in our facility. Give us a call.
